{"tid":838910,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"大J真係痴撚線，為左錢吹到行船入職4萬","createTime":"2018-09-27T13:15:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T14:12:04.000Z","uid":60635,"like":36,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"353d78d16e08984e800b3c00530c0a6f952b0701","tid":838910,"uid":60635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:15:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/Y20lOSz0zho\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FY20lOSz0zho&d=QFB8rg%2Bw8BgRi8i1z1WEUBv1o3X72Fc8dbph17rWX2c%3D&h=0cd302cc\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/Y20lOSz0zho</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n痴撚左線咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n讀完HD 做cadet先得果五百美金多D 仲要政府保貼幾千先夠一萬港幣，點撚樣4萬呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n要儲18個月sea time先可以考第一個牌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n放船無糧出唔撚駛計？比你升上三伙得兩萬幾一個月，一年放三個月船， 拉勻年薪少過aco啦<br />\n<br />\n一開波2~3萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n賺錢都比返小小良心啦，一個HD 要讀成兩年，落船簽約最少半年，大好青年比你呃三年時間走你過唔過意得去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7c7a24da40725ca4226098bdfcbce683c157c12","tid":838910,"uid":34444,"like":52,"dislike":1,"score":51,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-27T13:16:27.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">大家唔好中伏幫佢賺貼擊率 大J打手常用技倆嚟</span></span>"},{"pid":"12a9c